org.apache.calcite.rel.metadata

类 BuiltInMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.metadata.BuiltInMetadata

  • public abstract class BuiltInMetadata
extends Object
    Contains the interfaces for several common forms of metadata.
